This paper deals with natural language processing and information retrieval tasks such as hypernym detection and semantic similarity. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques and data mining, which are relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with semantic relationships between words, which is relevant to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves the analysis of Wikipedia articles, which is relevant to cs.CY (Computers and Society).
